Package: ggvita
Title: An R package for VIsualization and annotation of Tree Alignment.
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Meng Yuan", email = "dilimou26@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Jianrong Philip Yang", email = "jianrong.yang@outlook.com", role = c("aut"))
             )
Description:
  This package is for visualizing results calculated by the tree blasting algorithms which is developed by Pro.Yang Jianrong,SYSU. 
  'ggVITA' extends 'ggplot2' and 'ggtree' plotting system.
  Thanks for the ggtree package,the ggplot2 package and theirs authors:
  (1)ggplot2: Hadley and etc.
  (2)ggtree: Guangchuang Yu, David Smith, Huachen Zhu, Yi Guan, Tommy Tsan-Yuk Lam. 
  ggtree: an R package for visualization and annotation of phylogenetic trees with their covariates and other associated data. 
  Methods in Ecology and Evolution 2017, 8(1):28-36, doi:10.1111/2041-210X.12628
Depends:
  R (>= 3.3.2)
License: Artistic-2.0
